== The Freenode Forth Channel ==

The #forth channel on irc.freenode.net is a gathering place for realtime forth discussions. A mirror of past discussions is available at http://bespin.org/~nef/logs/forth/

----
=== Reading Material ===
* Introduction to Forth: http://tinyurl.com/kvawv
* Starting Forth: http://www.forth.com/starting-forth/
* Thinking Forth: http://tinyurl.com/nsy4j
* ANS/ISO Forth Standard doc: http://tinyurl.com/nx7dx

